# RNA feature 3D residue labels.
# Labels are created as independent grouped models under #317.2.
# Fetch and run the self-contained RNA label script from GitHub.
open https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mvorlander/spliceosome-structure-vis/main/scripts/label_scripts/5o9z_rna_labels.py
# Searchable named selection browser.
# In GUI ChimeraX this opens a small panel for selecting, zooming, and toggling RNA labels.
# Fetch and open the self-contained named selection browser from GitHub.
open https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mvorlander/spliceosome-structure-vis/main/scripts/selection_browser_scripts/5o9z_selection_browser.py
view
show nucleic
